RIYADH: Saudi Arabiaâ€™s Deputy Foreign Minister Waleed Al-Khuraiji met with Director of the UN Counter-Terrorism Center and the Office of Counter-Terrorism Dr. Jehangir Khan in the capital, Riyadh, on Wednesday.
	During the meeting, they reviewed the efforts between the Kingdom and the UN in many fields, including combating terrorism and extremism.
